headline: John Deere Honored as One of 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies®
summary: Deere & Company (NYSE: DE) has been named one of the 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies® by Ethisphere, marking its 18th recognition and distinguishing it as one of only 12 honorees in the Industrial Manufacturing industry. This accolade underscores Deere & Company's commitment to maintaining the highest standards of ethical business practices globally.
